<section class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>What is RTK Positioning?</h2>
    <p>
      Real-Time Kinematic (RTK) is a GNSS-based positioning technique that enhances accuracy from meter-level to centimeter-level by using real-time correction data. RTK systems rely on a reference station (CORS), a rover receiver, and a communication link that transmits correction data.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>


